# One scene, a whole wardrobe — paper is the light half of the pair (see
# noir.tape): same set, different lighting. The theme-aware bar shades
# itself: dark themes lighten it, light themes darken it — zero config.

Output paper.gif
# foley: dress paper

Set Width 700
Set Height 340
Set FontSize 16
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Type "echo 'same tape, dressed as: paper'"
Enter
Sleep 1200ms
Type "seq 1 3"
Enter
Sleep 2s
